<h1>About Us</h1>

<p>Welcome to FilmForge, where we bring you the latest and greatest in movies and TV series! We are dedicated to
    providing our users with a seamless and engaging platform to explore and discover entertainment content.</p>

<h2>Our Mission</h2>
<p>At FilmForge, our mission is to connect people with the content they love. Whether you are a fan of action-packed
    movies, heartwarming dramas, or thrilling TV series, we aim to provide an excellent viewing experience.</p>

<h2>What We Offer</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Movies:</strong> Discover a wide range of movies across different genres.</li>
    <li><strong>TV Series:</strong> Find your favorite TV shows, including both current and past seasons.</li>
    <li><strong>Trending Content:</strong> Stay up-to-date with the most popular movies and TV shows.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Our Story</h2>
<p>FilmForge was founded by a passionate group of entertainment enthusiasts who wanted to create a platform where users
    could easily discover movies and TV shows that match their interests. Over time, we have grown and continue to
    innovate to bring you an improved and personalized viewing experience.</p>

<h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
<p>Our team is made up of experienced professionals with a love for movies and technology. Together, we work hard to
    ensure that FilmForge continues to offer the best entertainment options to our users.</p>

